### GET /v1/profile/address/fetch

This endpoint retrieves the user's address details on the basis of different criteria, That can be provided as query parameters. Criteria parameters can be as follows:

1. id

2. userId

3. addressName

4. addressLine1

5. addressLine2

6. city

7. pincode

8. landmark

9. state

10. primaryAddress


#### Request

No request body parameters are required for this endpoint.

#### Response

The response is in JSON format and has the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "statusCode": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "responseBody": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "perPage": {
                    "type": "number"
                },
                "pageNo": {
                    "type": "number"
                },
                "sortBy": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "sortDirection": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "id": {
                                "type": "string"
                            },
                            "landmark": {
                                "type": ["string", "null"]
                            },
                            "addressLine1": {
                                "type": "string"
                            },
                            "addressLine2": {
                                "type": ["string", "null"]
                            },
                            "city": {
